{"type": "article", "id": 14498, "title": "松果瓣手包", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-06T07:12:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000325xBe7tgYIiJPpc05s.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t专门制作 3D 打印饰品的品牌 maison 203，邀请意大利的设计团队 odo fioravanti 设计了一款松果瓣手包。外表不规则的圆瓣就是模拟了松球的形状，巧妙地排列成对称的效果，具有立体的质感。手包由烧结尼龙材质制作，包内藏有磁扣，方便打开。目前正在巴黎家居装饰博览会展出，之后会上线出售。<a href=\"http://www.maison203.com/#\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142013gHjtyzL32WO4CiaJ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142013UegPJaidtcKZ8hfR.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142015wvphzuiSMxC3N4GI.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1227\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}